    "The main finding is the successful implementation of a blockchain and AI-based system for healthcare insurance fraud detection, which increases transparency and trust between insurance providers and subscribers.",
    "The conclusion highlights the potential of integrating wearable devices for real-time data collection and analysis in fraud detection systems while addressing challenges such as class imbalance, data standardization, and scalability.",
    "The research by Thesmar et al. (2019) explores the potential benefits and challenges of integrating artificial intelligence (AI) with healthcare claims data.",
